videos.description: Wyoming RB Trey Woods finds a hole and outruns the entire Hawaii defense to put the Cowboys up 7-0.
videos.headline: Woods darts up the middle for TD

videos.description: On fourth down on the goal line, Hawaii's Ryan Tuiasoa lowers his head and rumbles through the goal line to tie Wyoming 7-7.
videos.headline: Hawaii offense powers its way into end zone

videos.description: Hawaii QB Dru Brown is pressured, throws into traffic and gets intercepted as the Wyoming defense keeps the game tied 7-7 in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Red zone INT kills Hawaii drive

videos.description: Hawaii takes a 14-7 lead as RB Diocemy Saint Juste takes the ball for five yards past the goal line capping a scoring drive that was extended by a roughing the kicker penalty.
videos.headline: Hawaii's Saint Juste jets into end zone for TD

videos.description: One play after going down 14-7, Wyoming's Tyler Hall takes the kickoff 98 yards to the house and ties Hawaii late in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Wyoming responds with kick-return TD

videos.description: A pair of long runs set up Austin Conway to take a four-yard jet sweep into the end zone as Wyoming takes a 21-14 lead in the fourth.
videos.headline: Cowboys ride run game into end zone

videos.description: Hawaii QB Dru Brown connects with John Ursua on a seam route and Ursua outruns the Cowboys' secondary to tie Wyoming 21-21.
videos.headline: Ursua finds space in seam and scores

videos.description: Cowboys QB Josh Allen connects on a 25-yard score to James Price who slipped behind Hawaii's defense on the first play of over time.
videos.headline: Wyoming strikes on first play of OT

videos.description: Hawaii QB Dru Brown's pass is deflected and then intercepted by Cassh Maluia giving Wyoming the victory in a thrilling 28-21 finish.
videos.headline: Wyoming wins with interception in OT
